text: XHUACC-FM is a Mexican college radio station owned by the Universidad Autónoma del Carmen. ==History== XHUACC received its permit in February 2006, and at 11:15pm on December 12, 2006, test transmissions began for the new station on 88.9 MHz. ==References== Category:Radio stations in Campeche Category:University radio stations in Mexico
title: XHUACC-FM
